-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  The Least Common Multiple Calculator
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Build:
    ./build.sh              -- build lcm binary
    ./build.sh test         -- build lcm binary & run tests
    ./build.sh long test    -- build lcm binary & run all tests (takes long)
                               note: big1m test takes >5 min on i7-3720QM

Usage:
    ./lcm [THREAD_COUNT]    -- reads numbers from stdin, calculates Least
                               Common Multiple and prints it's multiples

Defaults:
    THREAD_COUNT is defaulted to the ammount of cores on the machine

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
